\v 1 Ngizaphakamisela amehlo ami\x + Hlab. 123.1.\x* ezintabeni, lapho usizo lwami oluzavela khona\x + Hlab. 87.1. Jer. 3.23.\x*.
\v 2 Usizo lwami luvela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + Hlab. 124.8. Hlab. 144.7.\x*, eyenza amazulu lomhlaba\x + Hlab. 115.15.\x*.
\v 3 Kayiyikuvuma ukuthi unyawo lwakho lutshelele\x + Hlab. 66.9. 1 Sam. 2.9.\x*; umlondolozi wakho\x + 121.4,5,7,8. Hlab. 41.2. 127.1. 145.20.\x* kayikuwozela\x + Hlab. 76.5.\x*.
\v 4 Khangela, umlondolozi kaIsrayeli\x + 121.4,5,7,8. Hlab. 41.2. 127.1. 145.20.\x* kayikuwozela njalo kayikulala\x + Hlab. 76.5.\x*\x + Isa. 5.27.\x*.
