\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* ingumlondolozi wakho\x + 121.4,5,7,8. Hlab. 41.2. 127.1. 145.20.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* ingumthunzi wakho\x + Hlab. 91.1. Nani 14.9.\x* esandleni sakho sokunene\x + Hlab. 16.8.\x*.
\v 6 Ilanga kaliyikukutshaya emini\x + Isa. 49.10. Isam. 7.16. Hlab. 91.5. 2 Kho. 4.19.\x*, lenyanga ebusuku\x + Jona 4.8.\x*.
\v 7 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakulondoloza kukho konke okubi\x + 121.4,5,7,8. Hlab. 41.2. 127.1. 145.20.\x*; izalondoloza umphefumulo wakho\x + 121.4,5,7,8. Hlab. 41.2. 127.1. 145.20.\x*\x + Hlab. 97.10.\x*.
\v 8 IN\nd kosi\nd* izalondoloza\x + 121.4,5,7,8. Hlab. 41.2. 127.1. 145.20.\x* ukuphuma kwakho lokungena kwakho, kusukela khathesi kuze kube phakade\x + Dute. 28.6. Nani 27.17.\x*.